data.description: This 3 BR/2 BA Cedar Hills home offers an open floor plan in the main living area with vaulted ceilings.  The master bedroom is over-sized with a walk-in closet.  Roof is only 2 years old and features architectural windows (dormers).  Home comes with a directional antenna, lots of channels to watch on TV.  A new, manual awning was just installed on the back deck.  It's a great spot to watch all the wildlife that likes to come visit.  The garage is currently outfitted with a handicap ramp, which is taking up part of one of the parking spots.  The backyard is wired with 220 amp power to accomodate a hot tub.
